- Feature/Domain-based Code Organization
- Organize directories not just by code type, but by feature/domain.
- Increase cohesion by keeping related files together.
- Example directory structure below:

src/
├── components/ # Shared/Common components
├── hooks/      # Shared/Common hooks
├── utils/      # Shared/Common utils
├── domains/
│   ├── user/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   └── UserProfileCard.tsx
│   │   ├── hooks/
│   │   │   └── useUser.ts
│   ├── product/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   └── ProductList.tsx
│   │   ├── hooks/
│   │   │   └── useProducts.ts
│   │   └── ...
│   └── order/
│       ├── components/
│       │   └── OrderSummary.tsx
│       ├── hooks/
│       │   └── useOrder.ts
│       └── ...
└── App.tsx